curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/8165' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8240-1/SGM8240-2/SGM8240-4", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8240-1 (single), SGM8240-2 (dual) and  SGM8240-4 (quad) are micro-power and high voltage  operational amplifiers, which are suitable for battery-  powered systems. These devices can operate from  2.7V to 24V single supply or from ±1.35V to ±12V dual  power supplies, and consume only 2.8μA quiescent  current per amplifier. They also provide rail-to-rail input  and output operation.  The SGM8240-1/2/4 provide low power, low bias  current and low noise. These devices fit in small  packages. The combination of the above features  makes them appropriate for various applications.  The SGM8240-1 is available in Green SOT-23-5 and  SC70-5 packages. The SGM8240-2 is available in  Green SOIC-8, MSOP-8 and TDFN-2×3-8L packages.  The SGM8240-4 is available in a Green SOIC-14  package. They are specified from -40℃ to +125℃  temperature range.        "}'
